msgctxt "talk00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>You a traveler?<2.pa>\n"
"I'm a fisherman of this village, but we're\n"
"in a bit of a bind lately.\n"
"<3.se_co>Monsters <4.re_co>have taken over the best\n"
"fishing spots.\n"
"\n"
"You used to be able to pull in a good\n"
"haul at <5.se_co>Aris Beach<6.re_co>, but these days you'd\n"
"be lucky to leave there with your life."
msgstr ""

