msgid ""
"<1.so>Heyyyyy! You took care of the <2.se_co>monsters<3.re_co>\n"
"at <4.se_co>Aris Beach<5.re_co>! <6.pa>It's been too long since\n"
"I've had a fish from those waters!\n"
"Thanks, mate. I suppose I should give\n"
"you this to show my appreciation."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
