"<1.so>Good stuff.<2.pa>\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Remember, it's called <3.se_co>Aris Beach<4.re_co>.<5.pa> The\n"
"<6.se_co>monsters <7.re_co>have set up shop there.\n"
"\n"
"Stay sharp."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk08"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Believe me, I'd love to...but I have a\n"
"family to look after. I can't be risking my\n"
"life.\n"
"If I had it my way, I'd be out there\n"
"skewering those monsters with this\n"
"harpoon."
msgstr ""

